des:
Ask for Facts, and learn about what really matters, like dark matter.

Facts skill provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "give me information about awesome wild facts

Alexa: The Facts skill can't help you with that. It can help you discover facts if you say tell me a fact. What can I help you with?

Say: tell me a soccer fact

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
